## Get cart — vacío
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{adminId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Response
// {"status":"success","code":200,"msg":"Request success","data":[],"timestamp":"2026-03-17 01:59:59"}


## Add item
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{userId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
    "id_product": 1,
    "quantity": 2
}

### Response
// {"status":"success","code":201,"msg":"Item added to cart","data":null,"timestamp":"2026-03-17 02:00:15"}


## Add same item again — debe acumular
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{userId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
    "id_product": 1,
    "quantity": 1
}

### Response
// {"status":"success","code":201,"msg":"Item added to cart","data":null,"timestamp":"2026-03-17 02:00:33"}


## Add second product
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{userId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
    "id_product": 11,
    "quantity": 1
}

### Response
// {"status":"success","code":201,"msg":"Item added to cart","data":null,"timestamp":"2026-03-17 02:00:44"}


## Get cart — con items
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Response
