## Update qty
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{userId}}/11
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
    "quantity": 5
}

### Response
// {"status":"success","code":200,"msg":"Quantity updated","data":null,"timestamp":"2026-03-17 02:01:22"}


## Update qty = 0 — debe eliminar el item
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{userId}}/11
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
    "quantity": 0
}

### Response
// {"status":"success","code":200,"msg":"Quantity updated","data":null,"timestamp":"2026-03-17 02:01:33"}


## Fail — más stock del disponible
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{userId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
    "id_product": 11,
    "quantity": 999
}

### Response
// {"status":"error","code":400,"msg":"Only 10 units available","data":null,"timestamp":"2026-03-17 02:01:45"}


## Get cart — con items
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Response
// {"status":"success","code":200,"msg":"Request success","data":[{"cart_item_id":13,"id_product":1,"quantity":4,"name":"Frieren: Beyond Journey's End Vol. 1","price":"12.99","stock":25,"active":1,"discount":"0.00","unit_price":"12.99","subtotal":"51.96","cover_image":"https:\/\/res.cloudinary.com\/dqemjiltd\/image\/upload\/v1771988013\/fbje1_zp63jy.jpg"}],"timestamp":"2026-03-17 02:02:19"}


## Remove item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{userId}}/13
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

